                "invention-title": [
                    "Heat supply-heat absorption integrated reaction device, reaction system, application and method for producing hydrogen from hydrogen-containing raw material",
                    "供热-吸热一体化的反应装置、反应系统和应用及含氢原料制氢的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of hydrogen energy and hydrogen energy storage, and discloses a heat supply-heat absorption integrated reaction device, a reaction system, application and a method for producing hydrogen from a hydrogen-containing raw material. The reaction device comprises an endothermic reaction part for endothermic reaction and a combustion reaction part which is arranged above the endothermic reaction part and is used for supplying heat to the endothermic reaction part by high-temperature flue gas generated by combustion; a partition plate for dividing the heat absorption reaction part into a heat absorption reaction chamber and a heat exchange flow guide chamber is arranged in the heat absorption reaction part, and a flue gas chamber is arranged in the heat exchange flow guide chamber; the combustion reaction part is provided with a combustion chamber communicated with the flue gas chamber, and the combustion chamber is communicated with a combustible raw material inlet and an air inlet; high-temperature flue gas generated by combustion of combustible raw materials mixed with air in the combustion chamber enters the flue gas chamber through the flue gas inlet to supply heat to an endothermic reaction generated in the endothermic reaction chamber. Through the integral reaction device, the heat of the catalytic combustion reaction is supplied to the heat absorption process, so that the energy consumption and the volume of the system are reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及氢能及氢储能技术领域，公开了一种供热‑吸热一体化的反应装置、反应系统和应用及含氢原料制氢的方法。该反应装置包括用于发生吸热反应的吸热反应部以及设置在吸热反应部上方用于将燃烧产生的高温烟气为吸热反应部供热的燃烧反应部；吸热反应部内部设置有将吸热反应部分隔为吸热反应室和换热导流室的分隔板，换热导流室内设置有烟气室；燃烧反应部设有与烟气室连通的燃烧室，燃烧室连通可燃原料进料口和空气进料口；与空气混合的可燃原料在燃烧室内燃烧生成的高温烟气通过烟气入口进入烟气室为吸热反应室内发生的吸热反应供热。本发明通过整体式反应装置，利用催化燃烧反应的热量来供给吸热过程，从而降低系统的能量消耗和体积。"
                }
